itemLabel: Estelle Morris, Baroness Morris of Yardley

wikipedia_page.main: Estelle Morris, Baroness Morris of Yardley, PC (born 17 June 1952), is a British Labour Party politician, who was the Member of Parliament (MP) for Birmingham Yardley from 1992 to 2005, and served in the Cabinet as Secretary of State for Education and Skills from 2001 to 2002.
